obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (30261)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title Definition.
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032&sectionId=30261&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires, each of the words and expressions`
  line `used herein and not defined but defined in the Representation of the People Act, 1950 (43 of 1950) shall`
  line `have the same meaning as in that Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (30262)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Creation of Legislative Council for Tamil Nadu.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032&sectionId=30262&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `(1) As from such date as the President may,`
  line `by order appoint,there shall be a Legislative Council for the State of Tamil Nadu; and as from that date,`
  line `in sub-clause (a) of clause (1) of ^1article 168, after the word "Karnataka", the words "Tamil Nadu" shall`
  line `be inserted.`
  line
  line `(2) In the said Council, there shall be 78 seats of which—`
  line
  line `(a) the numbers to be filled by persons elected by the electorates referred to in sub-clauses (a), (b)`
  line `and (c) of clause (3) of article 171 shall be 26, 7 and 7 respectively;`
  line
  line `(b) the number to be filled by persons elected by the members of the Legislative Assembly of`
  line `Tamil Nadu in accordance with the provisions of sub-clause (d) of the said clause shall be 26; and`
  line
  line `(c) the number to be filled by persons nominated by the Governor of Tamil Nadu in accordance`
  line `with the provisions of sub-clause (e) of that clause shall be 12.`
  line
  line `(3) As soon as may be after the commencement of this Act, the President, after consultation with the`
  line `Election Commission, shall, by order, determine,—`
  line
  line `(a) the constituencies into which the State of Tamil Nadu shall be divided for the purpose of`
  line `elections to the said Council under each of the sub-clauses (a), (b) and (c) of clause (3) of article 171;`
  line
  line `(b) the extent of each constituency; and`
  line
  line `(c) the number of seats to be allotted to each constituency.`
  line
  line `(4) As soon as may be after such determination, steps shall be taken to constitute the said Council in`
  line `accordance with the provisions of this Act, the Representation of the People Act, 1950 (43 of 1950) and`
  line `the Representation of the People Act, 1951 (43 of 1951).`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (30263)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Amendment of Third Schedule and Fourth Schedule to Act 43 of 1950.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032&sectionId=30263&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `In the Representation`
  line `of the People Act, 1950,`
  line
  line `(a) in the Third Schedule, after entry No. 6 relating to Karnataka, the following entry shall be`
  line `inserted, namely:`
  line
  line `"7. Tamil Nadu78 26 7 7 26 12";`
  line
  line `(b) in the Fourth Schedule, after the heading "KARNATAKA" and the entries thereunder, the`
  line `following heading and entries shall be inserted, namely:—`
  line
  line `"TAMIL NADU`
  line
  line `1. Municipalities, as referred to in article 243Q of the Constitution.`
  line
  line `2. Panchayat Union Councils.`
  line
  line `3. Cantonment Boards.`
  line
  line `4.District Panchayats referred to in the Tamil Nadu Panchayat Act, 1994 (Tamil Nadu`
  line `Act 21 of 1994).".`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (30264)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Amendment of section 15A of Act 43 of 1951.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032&sectionId=30264&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00032_201016_1517807325032
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `In section 15A of the Representation of the`
  line `People Act, 1951.— after the words and figures "under the Andhra Pradesh Legislative Council Act, 2005`
  line `(1 of 2006)", the words and figures "and constituting the Legislative Council of the State of Tamil Nadu`
  line `under the Tamil Nadu Legislative Council Act, 2010" shall be inserted.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
